\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/MLDM/110%2c%e8%8b%97%e7%b0%a1%2c811%2c20211015%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"MLDM,110,苗簡,811,20211015,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"苗簡","JNO":"811","JDATE":"20211015","JTITLE":"竊盜"}